association said the case posed problems because zeder failed to 
notify states legal office about the company 
there is basis for investigation at the very least jones 
said 
white house press secretary marlin fitzwater asked about 
zeders situation said today i dont have any details on it 
im sure fred will take care of that however is the appropriate 
way 
