a total of 30 million in economic development aid for micronesia 
and the marshall islands 
his firm island development was set up to solicit 
participation in development efforts in those areas and elsewhere 
in the pacific rim according to the companys incorporation papers 
the firm was incorporated on oct 14 1986 four days after 
