behagens award 
behagen who now lives and sells insurance in the atlanta area 
has been battling in federal court since 1982 with the amateur 
basketball association of the united states abausa and its 
executive director william wall 
the organization is now known as usa basketball 
behagen said the association violated federal antitrust law and 
his constitutional rights by playing a pivotal role in ending his 
career with a sienna italy team after he had left the national 
basketball association 
a federal jury in denver agreed and awarded him 684000 a 
