housing and other benefits from the italian team the league 
nominally had amateur status then and was accountable to the 
federation internationale de basketball amateur or fiba abausa 
was a member of fiba 
americans playing in the italian league were required to have a 
fiba license and a travel permit from the organization 
behagen returned to the united states in 1980 and signed a 
