house built by mennonites i cant even explain what its meant 
a few miles away in the hamlet of russellville arthur teives 
of newton kan is busy repairing another house 
teives who has been in south carolina five weeks said helping 
out has kind of been a way for me to serve god i feel this is 
where god wants me at this time in my life 
