manuel noriegas attorneys on monday filed a motion 
to withdraw from the case saying the government was trying to 
sabotage the defense by freezing the ousted panamanian leaders 
money 
trying a penniless noriega is like shooting fish in a 
barrel lead defense attorney frank rubino said the only thing 
the general owns at this time is essentially the clothes on his 
back 
us district judge william hoeveler set a meeting wednesday 
with federal prosecutors to discuss the issue rubino said he 
expected a hearing by the end of the week if the judge grants the 
motion that could delay the april 1991 trial 
prosecutors refused to comment on details of the motion but 
