and will earn 10 to 15 percent a year for investors the government 
corporation will not insure the earnings only the right of the 
investors to take their money back home hall explained 
private companies in the eastern european countries will be able 
to borrow from the fund and it will buy small quantities of their 
stock as a result the us government will become partial 
indirect owner of many private companies in countries which until 
